{"name":"Skinsplinterer","size":"large","type":"plant","tag":"","alignment":"chaotic evil","hitDice":"12","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"20","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"105 (10d10 + 50)","speedDesc":"30 ft., burrow 30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"5","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"5","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"90","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"5 (1,800 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"The [MON] can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The [MON] regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the earth elemental can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the earth elemental can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The earth elemental can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the earth elemental's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the earth elemental's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the earth elemental dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Land's Stride","desc":"The [MON] ignores difficult terrain made by plants."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes two attacks either with its slam or its rake."},{"name":"Slam","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack_: [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5ft, one target.\n_Hit_: [STR 1d12] bludgeoning damage."},{"name":"Rake","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack_: [STR ATK] to hit, reach 10ft, one target.\n_Hit_: [STR 1d8] slashing damage, and the creature is grappled."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Lash","desc":"Two creatures within 40ft of the [MON] must make a DC [STR SAVE] strength saving throw or be pulled 20ft towards the [MON]."},{"name":"Wall of Thorms","desc":"_1/day_: the [MON] can cast _Wall of Thorns_ as a 6th level spell."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"bludgeoning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"fire","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"},{"name":"poison","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"},{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"deafened"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"poisoned"},{"name":"unconscious"}],"languages":[{"name":"Elvish","speaks":false}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}